deps.context: find_package(wxwidgets components core aui adv webview)

libs.content: find_library(iconv_libraries names iconv libiconv libiconv-2 c)

find_library(sfml_${find_sfml_component_upper}_library_debug
                 names sfml-${find_sfml_component_lower}-d
                 path_suffixes lib64 lib
                 paths ${find_sfml_lib_paths})

find_library(sfml_${find_sfml_component_upper}_library_release
                 names sfml-${find_sfml_component_lower}
                 path_suffixes lib64 lib
                 paths ${find_sfml_lib_paths})

find_library(sdl2_library_temp
  names sdl2
  hints
  $env{sdl2dir}
  path_suffixes lib64 lib
  paths
  /sw
  /opt/local
  /opt/csw
  /opt
)

find_library(sdl2main_library
      names sdl2main
      hints
      $env{sdl2dir}
      path_suffixes lib64 lib
      paths
      /sw
      /opt/local
      /opt/csw
      /opt
    )
find_program( ndk_ccache "${_ndk_ccache}" doc "the path to ccache binary")
